column5: http://www.nrsweb.com/shop/product.asp?pfi...pleft_NRSGigbob  I'd get it if it were a little cheaper....

There are plenty of other toons out there that are more reasonably priced. They generally start around $350 and go up from there.  I have a OUTCAST FISH CAT COUGAR and it is a very good quality toon. Remember you get what you pay for. There is a good representation available through the Fishing Hole.  The Fishin' Hole
